"Returns a :ref:`KinematicCollision <class_KinematicCollision>`, which "
"contains information about a collision that occurred during the last "
":ref:`move_and_slide <class_KinematicBody_method_move_and_slide>` call. "
"Since the body can collide several times in a single call to "
":ref:`move_and_slide <class_KinematicBody_method_move_and_slide>`, you "
"must specify the index of the collision in the range 0 to "
"(:ref:`get_slide_count <class_KinematicBody_method_get_slide_count>` - "
"1)."
msgstr ""

